headline.main: Emily Post Is Dead Here at 86; Writer Was Arbiter of Etiquette; Author of Books and Columns on Good Manners -- Name a Synonym of Propriety Emily Post Is Dead Here at 86; Writer Was Arbiter of Etiquette

snippet: Mrs. Emily Post, for many years a leading authority on all matters of social good form, died Sunday in her apartment at 39 East Seventy-ninth Street after a brief illness. Her age was 86.
